title: CD to iPod Solution v6.4.2 Completed.rar
description:
CD to iPod Solution is a lightweight, fast, and powerful application for digitally extracting audio from CD-roms to iPod. It can extract audio files from CD and transmit them to your iPod easily. 

Besides, if the CD-rom unit on your computer supports Digital Audio Extraction and has an ASPI manager installed, CD to iPod Solution can directly read the audio from your music CD-roms and store it on your hard drive in either WAV, MP3 or Ogg Vorbis format.
